The Biblioteca Digital del Patrimonio Iberoamericano (BDPI, the Digital Library of Ibero-American Heritage, a cooperative project with Ibero-American National Libraries) allows users to access related Europeana content via a single link on their search results header. The idea is that the Europeana API serves as a bridge between European and Ibero-American heritage, thus connecting cultures through technology.
